ing this as a hard gate in CI. Out of scope for this step.\n- [medium] The script's `findLatestEvalResult()` picks the lexicographically last filename. Since filenames use the pattern `eval-<ISO-timestamp>.json` with colons replaced by dashes, this sorts correctly — but if any non-timestamp `.json` files were dropped in that directory, they could be picked erroneously. Out of scope.\n```\n\nVerdict: changes_made"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":626,"cacheRead":133049,"cacheWrite":224,"totalTokens":133900,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00939,"cacheRead":0.0399147,"cacheWrite":0.00084,"total":0.050147699999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774723639617,"responseId":"msg_01CmyxDZY1eKqAPcbrawHGFY"}}
